Môn: tiếng anh
PHẦN I. LISTEN AND CHOOSE THE BEST ANSWER (A, B, C or D):

Tom’s brother is _______.
A. slim
B. fat
C. short
D. tall
Đáp án: D. tall

Tom’s brother is wearing _______.
A. glasses
B. a blue T-shirt
C. a green T-shirt
D. green shorts
Đáp án: B. a blue T-shirt

Jenny’s sister has _______.
A. short hair
B. black hair
C. brown hair
D. long hair
Đáp án: D. long hair

Jenny’s sister is kind and _______.
A. friendly
B. helpful
C. funny
D. lazy
Đáp án: B. helpful

*1. Tom has one _______.
A. sister
B. brother
C. friend
D. uncle
Đáp án: A. sister

*2. Tom’s brother is _______ and really friendly.
A. funny
B. lazy
C. kind
D. mean
Đáp án: A. funny

*3. Jenny’s sister is _______ years old.
A. 18
B. 26
C. 16
D. 8
Đáp án: B. 26

*4. Jenny’s sister is _______.
A. fat
B. short
C. tall
D. slim
Đáp án: C. tall

