PHẦN III. SIGNS (BIỂN BÁO):

Look at the sign (P with car crossed out). What does this sign say?
A. You can’t park your car here.
B. You can park your car here.
C. There aren’t many cars here.
D. You can buy cars here.
Đáp án: A. You can’t park your car here.

Look at the sign (STOP). What does this sign say?
A. You must stop
B. You can’t stop
C. You can’t run
D. You can’t talk
Đáp án: A. You must stop

Look at the sign (P in circle crossed out). What does this sign say?
A. You can’t park your car here.
B. You can park your car here.
C. There aren’t many cars here.
D. You can buy cars here.
Đáp án: A. You can’t park your car here.

Look at the sign (No smoking). What does this sign say?
A. Smoking
B. No eating
C. No littering
D. No drinking
Đáp án: (Câu này biển báo là cấm hút thuốc nhưng đáp án không rõ ràng, có thể là lỗi đề, chọn B hoặc D nếu biển báo có hình ly/dĩa)

Look at the sign (OPEN FOR TAKEAWAY ONLY). What does this sign say?
A. You can eat in this restaurant.
B. This restaurant doesn’t open.
C. You can’t buy food here.
D. You can’t eat inside restaurant.
Đáp án: D. You can’t eat inside restaurant.

Look at the sign (CAUTION WET FLOOR). What does this sign say?
A. You can’t go
B. You must walk carefully
C. You can run faster
D. You will fall off
Đáp án: B. You must walk carefully

Look at the sign (SLOW CHILDREN AT PLAY). What does this sign say?
A. Children play here.
B. A park is nearby.
C. You shouldn’t go fast in this area.
D. Playing with the children is slow.
Đáp án: C. You shouldn’t go fast in this area.

Look at the sign (Keep Off The Grass). What does this sign say?
A. Don’t run in class.
B. Don’t step on grass.
C. No smoking
D. Take off your shoes
Đáp án: B. Don’t step on grass.

Look at the sign (No shoes). What does this sign say?
A. People don’t sell shoes in this place.
B. Please remove your shoes when you enter this place.
C. You can find shoes when you are in this place.
D. Don’t buy shoes when you enter this place.
Đáp án: B. Please remove your shoes when you enter this place.

Look at the sign (2m distance). What does this sign say?
A. Come together.
B. Stand up in two lines.
C. Go in pairs.
D. Keep two meters away from people.
Đáp án: D. Keep two meters away from people.

PHẦN IV. VERB FORMS (CHIA ĐỘNG TỪ):

Janet _______ (be) very happy when she gets lucky money.
Đáp án: is

Cần Thơ _______ (be) a city in the south of Vietnam.
Đáp án: is

