Đáp án: is

My brother and I _______ (be) students.
Đáp án: are

There _______ (be) a book on the desk.
Đáp án: is

There _______ (be) an airport in the city.
Đáp án: is

There _______ (be) many trees and flowers in my school garden.
Đáp án: are

There _______ (be) two chairs in the living room.
Đáp án: are

There _______ (be) a lot of pens on the table.
Đáp án: are

He _______ (not go) to the library after school on Sundays.
Đáp án: doesn't go

She _______ (not like) sports.
Đáp án: doesn't like

The children _______ (not go) to school at weekends.
Đáp án: don't go

Lisa and Toby _______ (not play) soccer every day.
Đáp án: don't play

