PHẦN V. MATCH THE ANSWERS TO THE QUESTIONS:
(Section 1)

What does she look like?

What’s she like?

Do you live in a house or an apartment?

Does she have any brothers or sisters?
A. She is funny.
B. We live in an apartment.
C. No, she doesn’t.
D. She is tall and slim.
Đáp án: 1-D, 2-A, 3-B, 4-C

(Section 2)

What is Mary like?

How often does Laura play volleyball?

Does your house have a big yard?

What are you doing this weekend?
A. I’m playing soccer with my brother.
B. Yes, it does.
C. Sometimes.
D. She is kind, active and sensitive.
Đáp án: 1-D, 2-C, 3-B, 4-A

(Section 3)

How often do you go running?

What time does the bus leave?

Who does the most housework in your family?

Do you usually go swimming on the weekends?
A. It leaves at 9:30 am.
B. My dad does.
C. Yes, I do.
D. I rarely go running.
Đáp án: 1-D, 2-A, 3-B, 4-C

(Section 4)

What time do you get up?

What does she look like?

What housework do you do?

How do the people prepare for Tet?
A. They decorate their houses.
B. I do the dishes.
C. She is tall and slim.
D. At 6:30.
Đáp án: 1-D, 2-C, 3-B, 4-A

(Section 5)

How much are those shoes?

Which club do you want to sign up for?

What's your favorite book?

Is he wearing glasses?
A. I want to sign up for Soccer Club.
B. They are $10.
C. Yes, he is.
D. I like Harry Potter.
Đáp án: 1-B, 2-A, 3-D, 4-C

PHẦN VI. READING (ĐỌC HIỂU):

A. Read the following passage. Decide if the statements are TRUE or FALSE:

People buy fruits and flowers before Tet.
Đáp án: True

During Tet, children wear new clothes and don’t get lucky money.
Đáp án: False

Everyone goes to works during Tet.
Đáp án: False

This holiday is very popular in Vietnam.
Đáp án: True

B. Read passage about Can Tho and check statements:

Cần Thơ is in the north of Vietnam.
Đáp án: False

It is famous for its floating markets and beautiful rivers.
Đáp án: True

The weather is cool in Cần Thơ.
Đáp án: False

Cần Thơ is an important center for business and transportation.
Đáp án: True

C. Read passage about Charlotte's Web and check statements:

Wilbur is a spider.
Đáp án: False

Mr. Zuckerman is kind.
Đáp án: False

Charlotte is a helpful spider.
Đáp án: True

Mr. Zuckerman thinks Wilbur is very funny.
Đáp án: False

